{"tid":2174493,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"IFixit 拆解 Galaxy Note 20 系列手機，或解釋為何手機會發熱","createTime":"2020-08-26T02:21:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T10:16:03.000Z","uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"11a671058eb818a79311798ae955d0266bf3f36d","tid":2174493,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T02:21:25.000Z","msg":"Samsung 推出 Galaxy Note 20 系列手機迎戰今年秋季手機大戰，有很多外媒開箱試玩的時候卻發現了一個問題，就是手機發熱燙手。iFixit 最近從一次 Note 20 的拆解，發現了發熱的可能成因。<br />\n<br />\niFixit 最近拆解了 Galaxy Note 20 和 Note 20 Ultra 手機，除了可以看到巨大的機背主相機的構造之外，還可以看到手機內部其他部分的構造，iFixit 意外地發現兩款手機都均沒有銅導熱管，並以多層石墨散熱膏取代，這與早前 JerryRigEverything 的發現相同，但奇怪的是有部分 Note 20 Ultra 會用銅導熱管散熱，同一款手機在散熱結構上可以完全不一樣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A6cuh9v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA6cuh9v.jpg&h=d4b07afe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就散熱結構不同，iFixit 推論有幾個原因，包括採用的處理器（Snapdragon 或 Exynos）不同、或是為新的散熱結構進行 A/B 測試等等。之不過，用兩種不同的散熱結構，可以導致什麼結果？目前 Samsung 官方未有確認，但從一些開箱試玩的網站已經可以感受到其影響，Android Authority、Wired UK 指 Note 20 使用時手機很熱，PCWorld 和 SamMobile 更分別錄得手機溫度達 100&deg;F 和 45-46&deg;C，反而 the Verge 網站開箱的 Note 20 Ultra 就沒有這種情況。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WjqGTH2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWjqGTH2.jpg&h=71157b27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNote 20 太多膠水，主機板像星戰角色<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y55GTH6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY55GTH6.jpg&h=235b4e96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這個謎題，可能要由 Samsung 解答了。另外 iFixit 逐一拆開 Note 20 系列手機部件，發現主機板有點像星戰中 AT-AT 的剪影。<br />\n<br />\n最後 iFixit 給予 Note 20 系列「可修復性評分」3 分，他讚揚 Note 20 螺絲種類少，只需一個螺絲批就能拆，很多部件模組化可以替換，但電池更換困難、螢幕維修繁瑣，而且膠水太多了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/enbKRuU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FenbKRuU.jpg&h=82c6c203&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1cf078897f24512109e9d74a6ad6d182fd09bb51","tid":2174493,"uid":12628,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T02:24:31.000Z","msg":"「Android Authority、Wired UK 指 Note 20 使用時手機很熱，PCWorld 和 SamMobile 更分別錄得手機溫度達 100&deg;F 和 45-46&deg;C，反而 the Verge 網站開箱的 Note 20 Ultra 就沒有這種情況。」<br />\n<br />\n有兩款，一款有銅導熱管散熱，一款得石墨散熱膏"},{"pid":"5c3008fbbe8a22b2e708fcd244c99c7029753a54","tid":2174493,"uid":124277,"like":2,"dislike":45,"score":-43,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T02:26:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"130c8bbfc02ee3bdfc9cd01527fe4b586edb1402","tid":2174493,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c3008fbbe8a22b2e708fcd244c99c7029753a54","tid":2174493,"uid":124277,"like":2,"dislike":45,"score":-43,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T02:26:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T02:37:35.000Z","msg":"咁啲三文魚唔尊重日本AV女優一樣咁仆街"},{"pid":"230fad691f22b782bc2d4bcf740d25bcc4eaca74","tid":2174493,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T02:58:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21471991fad3f7f6557289ba3253aa17fd0f03a0","tid":2174493,"uid":236891,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T03:03:08.000Z","msg":"會唔會熱到倒水電/爆炸？"},{"pid":"5c14fee515ed185d15aee920e844aa174dab11b4","tid":2174493,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T03:03:46.000Z","msg":"好在無換"},{"pid":"9f2d05d83f37e6db7db7361b478be5da8892a4ac","tid":2174493,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21471991fad3f7f6557289ba3253aa17fd0f03a0","tid":2174493,"uid":236891,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T03:03:08.000Z","msg":"會唔會熱到倒水電/爆炸？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T03:06:44.000Z","msg":"無案例"},{"pid":"d59b4b3b19e95ab0f5bddaa9debd5e554c774634","tid":2174493,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cf078897f24512109e9d74a6ad6d182fd09bb51","tid":2174493,"uid":12628,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-0